_sText:
surf_volcanic by Spy Complex

My first map, a gimmicky 1 minute t4 linear and a secret, also made by me, that could be used as a bonus.
Meant to be played with 66 tick, 3500 maxvel and 150 airacceleration.
Momentum start and endtriggers are built in.

Special Thanks to Hardex for making a rough outline for my name-brushwork, EarthwormEd for the showcase video and pretzl for the CS:GO port.
Big big thanks to Muta for repeated testing throughout all stages of developement, general help with mapping and the TF2 port.
